title: 12/09: Weekend Recap - How 'Bout Them Dolphins! (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
We're still buzzing about the finish in the NE-MIA game and we're trying to figure out the best nickname for that final play. We've also got the news and notes from Week 14 (3:20) and Winners (7:50) like Kenny Stills and Tom Brady and Losers (13:22) like Larry Fitzgerald and James White ... Checking in on those Waiver Wire RBs (16:50) and introduced a new game called "Hey, Just Sayin' ..." (20:40) with Doug Martin, Amari Cooper, Matt Ryan and more. Then we look at the Week 14 leaderboard at each position (27:18). TE was so predictable! ... A recap of each game with our Fantasy analysis (35:22) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
